<lb n="1"/>© svasti śrī jayābhyudayaṁ śakavarṣaṁ 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>bulu 1289 Agunēṁṭi plavaṁga saṁ<supplied reason="omitted">va</supplied>tsara Ā 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>śvīja śu 1 va <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> nāṁḍu śrīmanmahāmaṁḍaḷēsvara 
<lb n="4"/>Arirāyavibhāḷa bhāṣe getappuvarāyaragaṁḍa 
